## Notes for the board pack

- **Source of truth.** Every number above is traceable to the underlying
  evidence bundle (`evidence/{{ b.tenant }}-{{ b.generated_at[:10] }}.json`)
  signed at collection time. Auditors get the bundle; the board gets this page.
- **Cadence.** Re-running `csw-insights` weekly produces the trend line; the
  recommended cadence for board updates is monthly.
- **What this is not.** A posture score is a management tool, not a compliance
  attestation. Refer to the framework runbooks in `CSW-Compliance-Mapping` for
  control-by-control evidence.
